title: Ep. - 444 - DOMINIQUE DAWES DISCUSSES GOLDEN: THE JOURNEY OF USA’S ELITE GYMNASTS I AM GEORGINA AND LOVE IS BLIND 2
description:
Kate discusses Love is Blind 2 on Netflix and I am Georgina on Netflix, which follows the daily life of Georgina Rodriguez: mother, influencer, businesswoman, and partner to Cristiano Ronaldo.

 

Former Olympic gymnastics champion Dominique Dawes discusses Golden, the journey of USA’s Elite Gymnasts on Peacock TV, a six-part docuseries chronicling the journey of five elite American gymnasts as they headed to the Olympic Trials.  The series offers a glimpse of the rarely seen moments that high-level athletes endure in their personal lives, training and competitions.

 

Dawes also discusses the toxic culture of gymnastics, her experience with her own coach, and how parents can best protect their children involved in the sport. 

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
